The paper focuses on improving computer-aided detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the methods to medical imaging data sets suggests that it may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
